q - differnece between language , framework , library 

Language wo hoti hai jisme hum code likhte hain aur logic banate hain.
Framework us language par bana hota hai jo hume ready system deta hai taake app asaani se ban jaye.
Language basic hoti hai, framework kaam fast aur organized kar deta hai.
Jaise JavaScript language hai aur React us ka framework hai.






Official Release: The name was officially changed to "JavaScript" for its final release on December 4, 1995, as part of a joint announcement between Netscape and Sun Microsystems.






