â“ Interview Question 4
Blocking vs Non-Blocking kya hota hai?
Blocking

Kaam complete hone tak next kaam wait karta hai

Non-Blocking (Node.js)

Kaam background me chala jata hai

next kaam turant start ho jata hai




â“ Interview Question 3
